com.ekito.simpleKML.model
Class Coordinates

java.lang.Object
  com.ekito.simpleKML.model.Coordinates

public class Coordinates
extends java.lang.Object

A list of Tuples consisting of floating point values for longitude, latitude, and altitude (in that order). Longitude and latitude values are in degrees, where longitude ≥ −180 and <= 180 latitude ≥ −90 and ≤ 90 altitude values (optional) are in meters above sea level
